text: Pachole is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Dębowa Kłoda, within Parczew County, Lublin Voivodeship, in eastern Poland. It lies approximately north-east of Dębowa Kłoda, east of Parczew, and north-east of the regional capital Lublin. ==References== Pachole is also a sweet flat cookie from San Luis Potosí, Mexico Pachole
